Transform your browsing experience with the heartwarming 'Winnie the Pooh New Tab' extension! Every time you open a new tab, be greeted by delightful cartoonish images of Winnie the Pooh.

This charming extension brings a touch of childhood nostalgia and joy to your daily internet journey. The adorable animations of Pooh will not only brighten your day but also give your browser a unique and whimsical flair. Relive the magic of your favourite bear and his simple, honey-filled adventures with every new tab. Easy to install and absolutely delightful to use, 'Winnie the Pooh New Tab' is perfect for Disney fans and anyone who loves the gentle and comforting world of Pooh Bear. Add a sprinkle of Pooh's charm to your day, every day!
This extension uses Microsoft Bing  search engine on the New Tab.
Allows you to chose the default search engine.
